        {
            "title": "恒生去年股東應得溢利按年升3% 第4次中期息每股派3.2元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生銀行(00011)公布，2024年度全年股東應得溢利183.79億元，按年升3%；擬派第4次中期息維持每股3.2元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14717060-%e6%81%92%e7%94%9f%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e8%82%a1%e6%9d%b1%e6%87%89%e5%be%97%e6%ba%a2%e5%88%a9%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%873-%e7%ac%ac4%e6%ac%a1%e4%b8%ad%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af%e6%af%8f%e8%82%a1%e6%b4%be3-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230725_FI_source-bp_%E6%81%92%E7%94%9F%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C00011-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-19 12:25:47",
